4:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8","children":"LEAN Format is designed as a modern alternative to JSON, YAML, and XML for schema definition and data interchange. It combines the readability of YAML with the formality of JSON Schema."}]
